<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-16877] camel-salesforce: any salesforce operation inside transaction times out</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-16877</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;A transacted route with a salesforce operation will time out if it&apos;s called from a non-transacted route with a salesforce operation.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Reproducer here: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/jeremyross/camel-transacted-salesforce-reproducer&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/jeremyross/camel-transacted-salesforce-reproducer&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="13396155">CAMEL-16877</key>
            <summary>camel-salesforce: any salesforce operation inside transaction times out</summary>
